{"tid":1127772,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"呢 個 人 夫 嘅 背 影 真 係 好 正","createTime":"2019-04-27T10:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T13:04:16.000Z","uid":24160,"like":26,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fa967add2de06ca1965a22981c5ba447afc09d21","tid":1127772,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:38:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/27/182151_6ad9e2124041b60b5e989138faa639de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F182151_6ad9e2124041b60b5e989138faa639de.png&h=3ab3f388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人夫是個大隻佬，走過去自然要費事些。我本來要陪坐，他不肯，只好讓他自己坐。<br />\n<br />\n我看見他戴著黑布小帽，穿著貼身汗衫，深藍布質地，蹣跚地走到坐位邊，慢慢探身坐，尚不大難。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/27/182157_65080736f438ba501d95d2c3bcbd929c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F182157_65080736f438ba501d95d2c3bcbd929c.png&h=0e1a6b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他用兩手握著手機，兩腳再向上縮；他健碩的身子向左微傾，顯出雄偉的樣子。這時我看見他的背影，我的精很快地流下來了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/27/182202_6a61255154e3722724dea1a3ec3a44bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F182202_6a61255154e3722724dea1a3ec3a44bf.png&h=048d40d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我趕緊拭乾了精，怕他看見，也怕別人看見。我再向外看時，他已抱了朱紅的籃球準備下車了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/27/182209_19412304f424c19e123deb8b3c54e90d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F182209_19412304f424c19e123deb8b3c54e90d.png&h=b82ec5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n離開座位時，他先將厚大身軀挺直，慢慢站立，再擺動結實的二頭肌踏步而走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/27/182216_5166fd0767d77cdd6f5dacf8dced3cab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F27%2F182216_5166fd0767d77cdd6f5dacf8dced3cab.png&h=b49334c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我走了，到那邊短信！」我望著他走出去。他走了幾步，回過頭看見我，說，「到我家吧，裏邊沒人。」等他的背影混入來來往往的人裏，再找不著了，我便進來坐下，我的精液又來了。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ac30fedcf2eb24da8c0a02ff4380e154d6ace356","tid":1127772,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"係咁流我慢汁."},{"pid":"2ed896a88cf8073e46495539e58b2058ca2c2ad8","tid":1127772,"uid":2994,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d09dc904ba3d11efd6e0505fbdccd7248da5728","tid":1127772,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fc6fb70b084ce4a0f1e43be293973630b725a4","tid":1127772,"uid":126046,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:02:22.000Z","msg":"呀媽 係男人呀 仲要大大隻架<br />\n快啲黎睇啦"},{"pid":"4fd9e5c1f6e5eca910560f00b5544280de768606","tid":1127772,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed0e3a50880719fd0d800f43ae26ccdcbce3890","tid":1127772,"uid":232594,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T13:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}